{"tid":514742,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[4th Gen]召集所有90後車主司機","createTime":"2017-12-30T19:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T09:52:59.000Z","uid":46512,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1d7c12d1dd177d4576e4e1c17ee88fe83a950e","tid":514742,"uid":46512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T19:51:36.000Z","msg":"召集所有90後車主司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n經歷過3代90後車主群, 又係開新post招新人既時候<br />\n唔理你渣平車定貴車, 係老屎忽定新牌仔, 總之你對車有興趣<br />\n又想認識更多渣車既後生仔, 我地都歡迎你加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論你係之前入過群之後退左, 一直係個群入面, 定係未入過我地90後群<br />\n我地都歡迎你加入, 繼續帶旺90後群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有興趣入群既巴打請留下電話, 我會盡快加你入Whatsapp群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdrkJP2n-leiDOc6Cx0WHXnou6L6jTi7h0xJj9nF4vke0x1Qw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdrkJP2n-leiDOc6Cx0WHXnou6L6jTi7h0xJj9nF4vke0x1Qw%2Fviewform&d=%2BZXaqsG7MrZkzdzQz3wCy49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e493c34e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdrkJP2n-leiDOc6Cx0WHXnou6L6jTi7h0xJj9nF4vke0x1Qw/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"a28e1ab9d3cd78a8f621285c0621fcc400b56d31","tid":514742,"uid":13556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T21:39:17.000Z","msg":"ok join"},{"pid":"1e2bf049debc45d5e5035e3cafbe7469cdf995ad","tid":514742,"uid":75766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T22:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /